## TECH STACK — NON-NEGOTIABLE

- **Framework**: Next.js 14 with App Router (TypeScript, strict mode)
- **Database + Auth + Storage**: Supabase (use @supabase/supabase-js and @supabase/ssr)
- **AI Text Generation**: OpenAI API — model: gpt-4o for all writing and ideation
- **Image Generation**: OpenAI DALL-E 3 API — for book covers only
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui components
- **Document Compilation**: docx npm package (generates .docx files server-side)
- **State Management**: Zustand for client state, Supabase Realtime for live updates
- **Form Handling**: React Hook Form + Zod validation
- **Streaming**: OpenAI streaming via Vercel AI SDK (useChat, useCompletion)
- **Payments**: Stripe (subscription-based, free tier + Pro tier)
- **Deployment target**: Vercel

