## STYLING RULES

- **Aesthetic**: Dark editorial — deep navy/charcoal backgrounds, warm cream/gold typography, refined and literary feeling. Think high-end publishing house meets modern SaaS.
- **Font pairing**: Use `Playfair Display` for headings (serif, literary), `DM Sans` for body/UI
- Import both from Google Fonts in layout.tsx
- **Primary color**: `#C9A84C` (gold) for CTAs and accents
- **Background**: `#0F1117` (near black) with `#1A1E2E` for cards/panels
- **Text**: `#F0EAD6` (cream) for primary, `#8B8FA8` for secondary/muted
- All shadcn/ui components must be themed to match — update globals.css CSS variables accordingly
- Tailwind config must extend theme with these custom colors

