## API ROUTE RULES

- Every route in /app/api/ must validate the user session via Supabase before proceeding
- If no valid session: return 401 immediately
- All OpenAI calls must be wrapped in try/catch with proper error responses
- Use streaming (ReadableStream + TransformStream) for all text generation routes
- Rate limit: free tier = 1 book at a time, 3 total books; pro = unlimited
- Never expose API keys — all AI calls happen server-side only
- Log token usage to a separate `api_usage` table for billing/monitoring

