## KDP PUBLISHING INSTRUCTIONS (static content for ExportPanel)

Generate this content in the ExportPanel component as formatted JSX:

1. Create your KDP account at kdp.amazon.com
2. Click "Create" → "Kindle eBook" or "Paperback"
3. Enter your book title, subtitle, author name, and description
4. Set language, publication date, and add relevant keywords (7 allowed)
5. Choose 2 categories that best match your book
6. Upload your manuscript (.docx is accepted — upload the file you just downloaded)
7. Use KDP's previewer to review formatting
8. Upload your cover image (minimum 2560 x 1600px — use the cover you generated)
9. Set your pricing (70% royalty available for books priced $2.99–$9.99)
10. Select territories (choose "worldwide" unless you have regional restrictions)
11. Click "Publish" — your book goes live within 24-72 hours

