## BOOK COMPILATION (.docx format)

In /lib/docx/compiler.ts, the compiled book must include:

1. Cover page: Book title (large), Author name, Genre
2. Table of contents: Auto-generated with chapter titles
3. Each chapter: Chapter number + title as heading, full content, page break after
4. Back matter: "Published with ChapterAI" line (can be removed on Pro)

Use the `docx` npm package. All text from chapters is stored as markdown — convert to docx Paragraphs properly (handle ##, **bold**, *italic*, line breaks).

